.com/bestsellers/images/9781668249970.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;带我去见你的领袖 尼尔·德格拉斯·泰森&lt;br /&gt;这位天体物理学家描绘了与外太空外星人相遇的可能情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 23:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668249979?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>我不是机器人</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063446618?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780063446618.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《我不是机器人》作者：乔安娜·斯特恩&lt;br /&gt;这位荣获艾美奖的科技记者描述了一年来如何利用人工智能开展各种活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 23:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063446618?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>美国漫步者</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593537793?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780593537794.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;艾萨克·菲茨杰拉德的《美国漫步者》&lt;br /&gt; 《马萨诸塞州土袋》一书的作者踏上了长达一年的旅程，追随先驱苗圃工作者约翰尼·阿普尔塞德 (Johnny Appleseed) 的脚步。</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 23:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0593537793?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>美国的案例</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063360802?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9780063360808.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;美国案例 作者：Bret Baier&lt;br /&gt;福克斯新闻的首席政治主播分享了他对分裂时期我们民族性格的看法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 23:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/0063360802?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>美国宪法</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668221934?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781668221938.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《美国宪法》作者：Melissa Murray&lt;br /&gt; 《特朗普起诉书》的合著者为宪法中的每项修正案提供了历史背景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 May 2026 23:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668221934?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></ite